<P class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:57.35pt;">APPEAL from a judgment of the Ontario Court of Appeal
(Laskin, Simmons and Gillese JJ.A.), 2008 ONCA 139, 230 C.C.C. (3d) 472, 290
D.L.R. (4th) 655, 56 C.R. (6th) 163, 168 C.R.R. (2d) 193, 234 O.A.C. 101, 89
